    <!--
    ** Advanced - View specific configuration **
    The styles below can be overridden optionally to directly style a view in Parley. Note that it
    is required to override all the properties that are defined in the style. The default values, as
    configured here, can be used.

    ** Advanced - View specific fonts **
    To use different fonts for specific views, the style of that specific view should be overridden.
    Thus in turn, it should define every property as stated in this file. Thus to only change
    the font, copy the style definition of that view and only change the font property.
    -->

